        "Drop-off and pick-up areas"
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "Get to and from JFK Airport easily with the AirTrain, subway connections, and Long Island Railroad (LIRR).",
        "Licensed taxis are available outside each terminal at JFK. Flat-rate fares to Manhattan and other destinations are regulated for your convenience.",
        "Use apps like Uber and Lyft to get a ride to or from JFK. Follow signs to Ride App Pick-Up areas.",
        "Most rental car companies are located at Federal Circle, accessible via the AirTrain. Some operate from off-airport locations, but their shuttles also pick up at Federal Circle.",
        "Use one of our authorized shuttle, van or private car services to get to and from JFK.",
        "Use our designated areas for quick passenger drop-off, pick-up, or waiting in your vehicle. Options include curbside unloading, the pick-up and drop-off lot, and the cell phone lot for short stays."
      ],
